reviewText: Fun to watch old movie with private railcar.

I tried watching this film. I stopped at 15 minutes. It was confusing. The main mystery was is the lady really an heiress. Not much mystery. It wasn't funny. It was trying to emulate the thin man movies and the Toler Chans. It failed, IMO.
This is an entertaining film of the 30s.
Pretty much average affair here, somewhere between a mystery and a romance.  Typical 1930's stuff.
